  \{1,3,5\} \cup \{1,2,3\} = \{1,2,3,5\}, 
 \{1 ,3 , 5 \} \cap \{ 1 , 2, 3 \} = \{ 1, 3\}. 
 | \{ 1,3,5\}| = 3, 
 | \{ 1, 3\} | = 2. 
 |A \cup B| = |A| + |B| - |A \cap B|. 
